results.name: Predator Freak.3 TF J 'Demonscale - Black White'
adidas Yeezy 500 High Shale Warm
results.story: The adidas Yeezy 500 High ‘Wakaran’ showcases neutral beige tones on a flexible elastane upper, equipped with a comfortable padded collar and reinforced with suede and leather overlays. Reflective piping delivers added visibility in low-light conditions. Progressively darker shades of grey distinguish the podular adiPRENE+ midsole and rubber outsole, featuring a wavy traction pattern for optimal grip. The exterior is stripped of distinguishing logos and trademarks, relegating the sneaker’s branding elements to the sockliner instead.

results.name: adidas Yeezy 500 High Mist Slate
results.story: The adidas Yeezy 500 High ‘Mist’ delivers an understated colorway of the retro-inspired silhouette that borrows tooling from Kobe Bryant’s KB8 3, itself modeled after the brand’s Feet You Wear cushioning technology. Up top, grey elastane is fortified with tonal suede and leather overlays that reveal a subtle greenish cast. Reflective piping traces the wavy lines of the mudguard, while a grey rubber wrap provides added durability. A matching grey adiPRENE+ midsole delivers impact absorption and a smooth ride.

results.name: Predator Freak.3 Laceless TF 'Demonscale - Black White'
Disney x Court Rallye Slip J 'Polka Minnie'
Stan Smith 'Sharpie Pack - Graffiti White Green'
adidas NMD R1 Cloud White Orbit Grey (W)
Wmns Five Ten Freerider 'Black Acid Mint'
adidas Ultra Boost DNA Jordan E Moss
ZX 9000 'A-ZX Series - YCTN'
results.story: The adidas ZX 9000 ‘YCTN’ represents the letter ‘Y’ in the brand’s ‘A-ZX Series,’ spanning 26 distinct drops throughout 2020 and 2021 that explore the legendary ZX running franchise. Named after the Yucatan and inspired by traditional moccasin style footwear, this pair carries a mostly black upper crafted from a premium blend of suede, leather and nubuck. Contrast Z-shaped stitching encircles the toe box of the right shoe, while X-shaped stitching adorns the left.

results.name: adidas NMD Hu Pharrell Williams Cream
results.story: Limited to just 250 pairs, the Pharrell x adidas NMD Human Race ‘Cream’ shows off a design refresh, highlighted by a unique rib-knit upper. The off-white textile construction is accented with a pink leather heel tab and wraparound rope laces. Down the vamp, ‘Human Race’ is spelled out in embroidered Korean lettering. The lightweight build is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, its lateral sidewall embellished with EVA plugs in contrasting cream and blue.

results.name: Swift Run X J 'Clear Mint Iridescent'
Arizona x Superstar 'Have an Iced Day - Teal Yellow'
results.story: Launching as part of a four-piece collection centered around the popular beverage brand, the Arizona x adidas Superstar ‘Teal Yellow’ showcases mismatched color blocking on the all-leather upper. The right shoe features a bright teal finish on the tongue and lateral side panel, while the medial side is rendered in a subtle Chalk White tone. The left shoe features pink and mint green hues in the same areas. Metallic lace jewels depict a smiley face with the tagline ‘Have an Iced Day,’ a slogan that’s repeated on the icy outsole of the left shoe.

results.name: 4D Fusio 'Sunset'
results.story: The adidas 4D Fusio ‘Sunset’ combines a vibrant palette with the brand’s groundbreaking 3D-printed tooling. Contrasting off-white and orange fibers make up the composition of the Primeknit textile upper, secured with an integrated lacing system that incorporates a series of translucent tubes affixed to the sneaker’s side panels. Finely tuned cushioning comes courtesy of the lattice-like 4D midsole, finished in purple and partially wrapped in an orange and pink TPU belt that extends from the toe and around the heel.

results.name: Arizona x Superstar 'Have an Iced Day - Teal White'
results.story: The Arizona x adidas Superstar ‘Teal White’ is taken from a four-piece collection featuring unique branding elements drawn from the iced tea brand. The iconic low-top makes use of a bright teal leather upper, marked with a debossed Aztec print and colorful embroidered graphics. An Arizona logo lands on the heel tab, while the company’s ‘Have an Iced Day’ tagline is integrated into smiley face lace jewels. The slogan is repeated on the translucent outsole of the left shoe.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 2021 Triple White
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 ‘Cloud White’ offers a blank-slate colorway of the performance running shoe that packs more Boost and energy return than its predecessor. The sneaker’s breathable knit upper, partially made with recycled Primeblue materials that include Parley Ocean Plastic, sits on a full-length Boost midsole built with 6% more Boost capsules than the UltraBoost 20. Underfoot, a new Torsion system dubbed Linear Energy Push increases forefoot bending stiffness by 15%, yielding a more responsive ride.

results.name: Arizona x Superstar 'Have an Iced Day - Chalk White'
results.story: Launching as part of a collaborative pack with the iced tea brand, the Arizona x adidas Superstar ‘Chalk White’ updates the sneaker icon with refreshed branding elements, icy translucent outsoles and added pull tabs at the heel. Arizona’s Aztec-inspired graphic is debossed throughout the off-white leather upper, contrasted by a burst of bright teal coloring on the collar lining. A smiley face lace jewel features the beverage company’s ‘Have an Iced Day’ slogan, which makes a repeat appearance on the outsole of the left shoe.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 2021 Halo Silver
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 ‘Halo Silver’ treats the lightweight running shoe to a subdued greyscale makeover, one that allows the sneaker’s performance capabilities to claim the spotlight. They include a reconfigured Boost midsole that packs 6% more Boost capsules than the shoe’s predecessor, along with a revised Torsion system that increases forefoot rigidity to deliver a more responsive run. Up top, the knit upper continues adidas’ sustainability efforts with the inclusion of Parley Ocean Plastic and other recycled high-performance materials.

results.name: adidas Dame 7 Rip City Cloud White
results.story: The adidas Dame 7 ‘Cloud White’ dresses Damian Lillard’s seventh signature shoe in a familiar color scheme redolent of the Portland Trail Blazers. The upper is constructed from perforated white textile, reinforced with tonal synthetic leather overlays and secured with an integrated lacing system. A plush tongue combines with foam pods built into the interior lining to deliver a comfortable fit. The sneaker rides on a full-length Lightstrike midsole, good for springy cushioning on the hardwood.

results.name: Wmns ZX 2K Boost 'Grey Crew Blue'
results.story: The adidas women’s ZX 2K Boost ‘Grey Crew Blue’ highlights subtle pops of color on an otherwise neutral rendition of the responsive lifestyle runner. An integrated lacing system secures the grey textile upper, accented with blue three-stripes, a yellow forefoot overlay, pink collar binding and a peach-colored heel tab. The streamlined build is supported by a full-length Boost midsole, partially enveloped in a matching grey TPU cage for added durability and support.

results.name: Predator Freak.4 FG 'Royal Blue'
results.story: A performance soccer cleat built for firm ground and artificial grass, the adidas Predator Freak.4 FG ‘Royal Blue’ carries a soft synthetic upper secured with traditional lacing. A gradient blend of black and royal blue is applied to the seamless build, featuring a textured surface for enhanced ball control. The streamlined silhouette is mounted on a neon green TPU plate, outfitted with triangular studs that dig into the ground for maximum traction.

results.name: Swift Run X Infant 'White Iridescent'
results.story: The adidas Swift Run X Infant ‘White Iridescent’ delivers running shoe comfort for little feet. Inspired by archival track shoes, the sneaker makes use of a white textile upper with iridescent purple three-stripes. Interior bootie construction provides a snug, comfortable fit, while an EVA midsole offers lightweight cushioning with each step. Underfoot, flex grooves are built into the black rubber outsole, resulting in a traction pattern that promotes the natural motion of the foot.

results.name: Superstar 'White Splatter'
results.story: The adidas Superstar ‘White Splatter’ treats the sneaker icon to a colorful makeover. A hectic paint-splatter print is applied to the heel tab and signature three-stripes, allowing the details to stand out against a crisp white leather upper. Additional embellishments take the form of metallic gold branding hits, including a Superstar wordmark stamped on the lateral quarter panel. The low-top is mounted on a sturdy rubber cupsole, featuring a classic herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Freak MD 'White Team Power Red'
results.story: The adidas Freak MD ‘White Team Power Red’ delivers a performance football cleat built with cushioned comfort. Metallic crimson three-stripes adorn the durable white synthetic upper, equipped with a padded mesh tongue for added breathability. An anatomically molded EVA sockliner combines with a Bounce midsole for lightweight cushioning. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a molded lug pattern for maximum grip on the turf.

results.name: Terrex Trailmaker 'Green Oxide'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Trailmaker ‘Green Oxide’ showcases muted earth tones on an outdoor shoe made for light hikes and non-technical trails. Mossy green textile is utilized on the upper, reinforced with no-sew synthetic overlays at the toe and heel. A midfoot cage offers added support and a feeling of lockdown. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a full-length EVA midsole, reinforced underfoot by a lugged Traxtion outsole for sure footing on uneven terrain.

results.name: S2G 'Grey White'
results.story: The adidas S2G ‘Grey White’ delivers a streamlined golf shoe built with sustainability in mind. Recycled polyester is utilized on the waterproof textile upper, reinforced with synthetic white leather on the eyestay and heel overlay. The minimalist build is mounted on a full-length Bounce midsole for lightweight cushioning and flexibility. Underfoot, the spikeless Adiwear outsole features a V-shaped Traxion pattern for superior grip on slick greens.

results.name: Terrex Skychaser XT Mid GTX 'Black Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Skychaser XT Mid GTX ‘Black Solar Yellow’ combines responsive cushioning with a durable build designed to withstand the elements. A drawcord lacing system secures the black textile upper, reinforced with tonal synthetic overlays and a waterproof Gore-Tex lining. The high-top rides on a full-length Boost midsole, featuring an EVA frame and TPU Pro-moderator for enhanced stability and support. Underfoot, a lugged Continental rubber outsole delivers reliable traction on rugged terrain.

results.name: Terrex Trailmaker Mid GTX 'Wild Moss'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Trailmaker Mid GTX 'Wild Moss' applies muted earth tones to an outdoor shoe built for all-conditions wear. The textile upper is bolstered with seamless forefoot overlays, a supportive midfoot cage and an external heel counter. Additionally, a waterproof Gore-Tex membrane keeps feet dry during inclement weather. The sneaker-boot hybrid rests on a full-length EVA midsole, reinforced by a lugged Traxtion outsole for optimal grip on rough terrain.

results.name: adidas NMD R1 HER Studios Floral (W)
results.story: The Her Studio London x adidas women’s NMD_R1 ‘Floral’ treats the lifestyle runner to a graphic-intensive makeover, courtesy of the textile print studio based in East London. The sneaker’s one-piece black textile upper is offset by a contrasting red pull tab and a multi-color floral print on the heel patch and signature three-stripes. The sock-like upper sits on a full-length Boost midsole, its lateral sidewall fitted with EVA plugs in contrasting teal and black hues.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost 5.0 DNA Halo Ivory (W)
D.O.N. Issue #2 J 'Clear Mint'
results.story: Built for big kids, the adidas D.O.N. Issue #2 J ‘Clear Mint’ updates Donovan Mitchell’s second signature shoe with a vibrant palette designed to stand out on the basketball court. A bright turquoise hue floods the breathable mesh upper, secured with an integrated lacing system for midfoot lockdown. Screaming Pink accents land on the sneaker’s branding elements, including Mitchell’s personal logo on the molded heel overlay. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a podular Bounce midsole.

results.name: adidas T-Mac 2 Restomod White Royal Blue
results.story: The 2021 edition of the adidas T-Mac 2 EVO ‘White Royal’ brings back Tracy McGrady’s second signature shoe, originally released in 2003 and featuring a simple two-tone color scheme reflecting the athlete’s early years with the Orlando Magic. The streamlined silhouette makes use of a white leather upper with perforated detailing and radiating blue lines throughout the forefoot. The sneaker’s updated tooling utilizes a Bounce midsole, reinforced underfoot with a traditional herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: EQT Primegreen 'Cloud White'
results.story: The adidas EQT Primegreen ‘Cloud White’ presents a pristine colorway of a spikeless golf shoe built with responsive cushioning. The waterproof upper, comprising a blend of breathable white mesh with tonal synthetic overlays, is made in part with Primegreen, a series of high-performance recycled materials. The lace-up rests on a full-length Bounce midsole with a Boost insert in the heel for enhanced cushioning. Underfoot, the Adiwear outsole is equipped with an integrated traction pattern.

results.name: T-MAC 2.0 EVO Core Black
results.story: The adidas T-Mac 2 EVO ‘Black Royal’ brings back an OG colorway of Tracy McGrady’s second signature shoe, originally released in 2003 and updated with contemporary tooling. The black leather upper is accented with molded royal blue lines that extend from the lateral midfoot and sweep over the toe box. Interior bootie construction delivers a snug, comfortable fit. The sneaker rides on a responsive Bounce midsole, supported underfoot by adidas’ Torsion system and a herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Alphatorsion 'Acid Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Alphatorsion ‘Acid Yellow’ dresses the versatile running shoe in fluorescent colors designed to make a statement. A vibrant yellow finish distinguishes the textile upper, fortified with translucent overlays and accented with oversized Torsion System branding. The lightweight build is placed atop a matching yellow Bounce midsole, reinforced underfoot by a high-traction blue rubber outsole and adidas’ stabilizing 360-degree Torsion System.

results.name: S2G 'Crew Blue'
results.story: The adidas S2G ‘Crew Blue’ highlights a monochromatic finish on a spikeless golf shoe that borrows cushioning technology from the brand’s running line. Recycled content is blended into the composition of the textile and microfiber upper, reflecting adidas’ commitment to eliminating plastic waste. The streamlined build sits atop a full-length Bounce midsole, good for springy cushioning with each step. Underfoot, the Adiwear outsole features a V-shaped Traxion pattern for superior grip on the green.

results.name: Wmns Five Ten Freerider Primeblue 'Acid Mint Gum'
results.story: The adidas women’s Five Ten Freerider Primeblue ‘Acid Mint Gum’ treats the mountain biking shoe to a simplistic two-tone color scheme. A subdued teal finish is applied to a breathable textile upper made in part with Primeblue, featuring high-performance recycled materials that include Parley Ocean Plastic. The sneaker is mounted on a one-piece gum rubber cupsole, equipped with a distinctive Dotty tread keep designed to keep feet planted on the pedals.

results.name: Superstar 'Black Camo'
results.story: The adidas Superstar ‘Black Camo’ updates the iconic silhouette with eye-catching graphic-print accents. They take the form of a multicolor camo-like design on the heel tab and signature three-stripes, allowing the details to stand out against a stark black leather backdrop. ‘Superstar’ is stamped in gold foil lettering on the lateral quarter panel, matching adidas branding hits on the tongue and heel tab. A clean white rubber cupsole anchors the shell-toed sneaker.

results.name: Her Studio London x Wmns Sleek 'Floral'
results.story: The Her Studio London x adidas women’s Sleek ‘Floral’ updates the lifestyle silhouette with embroidered blossoms on the lateral side panel. The floral graphics, provided by the textile print studio based in East London, stand out against a dark navy leather backdrop. Soft pastel accents land on the heel tab and adidas logo window on the lateral eyestay. The low-top rests on a white rubber midsole, supported by an old-school herringbone traction outsole.

results.name: Terrex Trailmaker 'Black Aluminium'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Trailmaker ‘Black Aluminium’ dresses the outdoor silhouette in an entirely neutral color palette. A black and grey textile upper is fortified with no-sew forefoot overlays and an external heel counter for rearfoot stability. Rope laces are integrated into the supportive midfoot cage to deliver a lockdown fit. The hiking shoe is placed atop a lightweight EVA midsole, reinforced by a Traxion rubber outsole with V-shaped lugs for sure footing on uneven ground.

results.name: Terrex Trailmaker 'Black Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Terrex Trailmaker ‘Black Solar Yellow’ showcases vibrant accents on an outdoor silhouette designed for light outdoor adventures. The upper features a running shoe build, highlighted by breathable black textile with synthetic overlays, a supportive midfoot cage and external heel counter. A wider forefoot shape and an EVA support frame combine to deliver a stable ride through uneven terrain. Underfoot, the lugged Traxion rubber outsole provides optimal grip in all directions.

results.name: Wmns Superstar 'Heart Logo - White'
results.story: The adidas women’s Superstar ‘Heart Logo’ updates the iconic sneaker with luxe details and refreshed branding elements. The low-top makes use of a crisp white leather upper, accented with contrasting black velvet on the heel tab and signature three-stripes. They’re joined by an adidas Trefoil and an accompanying heart graphic embroidered on the lateral heel. The sneaker rides on a standard rubber cupsole, outfitted with a herringbone traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Harden Stepback 2 'Solar Red'
results.story: The adidas Harden Stepback 2 ‘Solar Red’ showcases an energetic color scheme guaranteed to command attention on the hardwood. An integrated lacing system secures the bright orange textile upper, reinforced with a series of contrast hued overlays and a royal blue heel counter marked with James Harden’s personal logo. Floating multicolored three-stripes extend into the lightweight Bounce midsole, supported underfoot by a grippy rubber outsole

results.name: Delpala 'White Black'
results.story: The adidas Delpala ‘White Black’ updates the skate-inspired low-top with an essential color palette that amplifies the shoe’s no-frills aesthetic. Breathable white canvas makes up the composition of the one-piece upper, accented with contrasting black three-stripes and a grey suede heel tab. The low-profile sneaker rests on a vulcanized rubber midsole, supported by a rubber outsole that incorporates adidas Trefoils in the traction pattern.

results.name: Busenitz Vintage 'Core Black'
results.story: The adidas Busenitz Vintage ‘Core Black’ offers a monochromatic take on the skate shoe inspired by the Copa Mundial soccer boot. The upper is constructed from stitched black suede, accented with matching black textile on the heel tab and signature three-stripes. ‘Busenitz’ is stamped in gold foil lettering on the lateral quarter panel. Underfoot, an Adiprene sockliner delivers lightweight cushioning. The low-profile silhouette is mounted on a contrasting off-white rubber cupsole.

results.name: Wmns Nizza RF Platform 'Heart Embossed - Scarlet'
results.story: The adidas women’s Nizza RF Platform ‘Heart Embossed’ treats the reinvented retro hoops shoe to a simplistic two-tone color scheme. The scarlet leather upper is accented with contrasting white leather on the heel tab and signature three-stripes, the latter components enlivened with a tonal print made up of embossed hearts and Trefoils. The pattern is repeated on the sockliner, while the sneaker’s top eyelets are rendered in heart-shaped form. A towering platform midsole anchors the low-profile silhouette.

results.name: SolarGlide ST 'Black Blue Oxide'
results.story: The adidas SolarGlide ST ‘Black Blue Oxide’ highlights reflective three-stripes on a responsive running shoe that delivers a stable ride. The engineered mesh upper incorporates Primegreen, a series of recycled high-performance materials, as well as stitched-in reinforcements for lightweight support. The sneaker sits atop a full-length Boost midsole, partially enclosed in a Stable Frame for enhanced stability. Underfoot, the Stretchweb outsole is built with grippy Continental rubber.

results.name: Wmns Sleek 'Heart Embossed - White Scarlet'
results.story: The adidas women’s Sleek ‘Heart Embossed’ adds subtle romantic details to the minimalist silhouette, highlighted by white leather upper covered in a tonal all-over print made up of embossed hearts and adidas Trefoils. The sneaker’s top eyelets are shaped like hearts and painted red, matching the heel tab and adidas branding on the lateral logo window. Additional details include perforated three-stripes and a classic herringbone traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Adilette Slide 'Glow Blue'
results.story: The adidas Adilette Slide ‘Glow Blue’ gives the warm-weather staple a simple two-tone finish. White three-strip detailing wraps across the wide bandage upper, coated in quick-drying polyurethane and lined in soft textile for abrasion-free comfort. Additional details include a contoured footbed and a lightweight EVA midsole, its lateral sidewall embossed with adidas branding. Underfoot, the textured outsole provides grippy traction on wet or dry surfaces.
